.cl-expunge">CL_EXPUNGE</a></span></strong>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.imap-delete-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>    <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">imap</span></dt><dd><p class="para"><span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.imap-connection.php" class="classname">IMAP\Connection</a></span> 实例。</p></dd>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">message_nums</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       A <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span> representing one or more messages in IMAP4-style sequence format       (<span class="literal">"n"</span>, <span class="literal">"n:m"</span>, or combination of these       delimited by commas).      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">flags</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       You can set the <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/imap.constants.php#constant.ft-uid">FT_UID</a></span></strong> which tells the function       to treat the <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">message_nums</span> argument as a       <span class="literal">UID</span>.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.imap-delete-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   总是返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.true">true</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 errors" id="refsect1-function.imap-delete-errors">  <h3 class="title">错误／异常</h3>  <p class="para">   Throws a <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.valueerror.php" class="classname">ValueError</a></span> if <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">flags</span>   is invalid.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1