hp.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.true">true</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 errors" id="refsect1-function.imap-clearflag-full-errors">  <h3 class="title">错误／异常</h3>  <p class="para">   Throws a <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.valueerror.php" class="classname">ValueError</a></span> if <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">options</span> is invalid.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.imap-clearflag-full-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">imap</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.imap-connection.php" class="classname">IMAP\Connection</a></span>  实例，之前接受有效的 <span class="literal">imap</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>     <tr>      <td>8.0.0</td>      <td>       A <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.valueerror.php" class="classname">ValueError</a></span> is now thrown on invalid       <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">options</span> parameter values. Previously,       a warning was emitted and the function returned <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>.      </td>     </tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div>  <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.imap-clearflag-full-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link imap_setflag_full()} - Sets flags on messages</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
*
 * Clears flags on messages
 * @link https://php.net/manual/zh/function.imap-clearflag-full.php
 * @param resource $imap
 * @param string $sequence <p>
 * A sequence of message numbers. You can enumerate desired messages
 * with the X,Y syntax, or retrieve all messages
 * within an interval with the X:Y syntax
 * </p>
 * @param string $flag <p>
 * The flags which you can unset are "\\Seen", "\\Answered", "\\Flagged",
 * "\\Deleted", and "\\Draft" (as defined by RFC2060)
 * </p>
 * @param int $options [optional] <p>
 * <i>options</i> are a bit mask and may contain
 * the single option:
 * <b>ST_UID</b> - The sequence argument contains UIDs
 * instead of sequence numbers</p>
 
#[LanguageLevelTypeAware(['8.3' => 'true'], default: 'bool')]
*/
function imap_clearflag_full(#[LanguageLevelTypeAware(['8.1' => 'IMAP\Connection'], default: 'resource')] $imap, string $sequence, string $flag, int $options = 0) {}

